                    "existingWordIds", existingWordIds
            ));
        }
    }

    @GetMapping("/todaylist")
    public List<TodayPlan> getTodayPlan(@RequestParam Integer userId) {
        return todayPlanService.getTodayPlan(userId);
    }

    @PostMapping("/delete")
    public void deleteWordsFromPlan(@RequestBody AddWordsRequest request) {
        todayPlanService.deletePlansByIds(request.getUserId(), request.getWordIds());
    }
}
